## 2. settings.local.json（项目级 Claude 标准配置）

```json
{
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN": "YOUR_TOKEN",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic",
    "API_TIMEOUT_MS": "3000000",
    "CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC": "1",
    "ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL": "glm-5-turbo",
    "ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL": "glm-5.1",
    "ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL": "MiniMax-M2.7",
    "ANTHROPIC_MODEL": "glm-5-turbo"
  },
  "permissions": {
    "allow": [
      "Bash(python3 -m py_compile <PROJECT_PATH>/src/commands/usemodel/snake_launcher.py)",
      "mcp__codex__codex",
      "Bash(python3 -m py_compile <PROJECT_PATH>/templete/v1/snake_main.py)",
      "Bash(python3 -m py_compile snake_engine.py snake_main.py)"
    ]
  },
  "model": "MiniMax-M2.7",
  "enabledPlugins": {
    "ralph-wiggum@claude-code-plugins": true
  },
  "extraKnownMarketplaces": {
    "claude-code-plugins": {
      "source": {
        "source": "github",
        "repo": "anthropics/claude-code"
      }
    }
  },
  "skipDangerousModePermissionPrompt": true
}
```

## 3. settings.likecode.json（用户级全局 likecode 默认配置）

放置路径：`~/.claude/settings.likecode.json`

内容与 `settings.likecode.local.json` 结构相同，可作为跨项目的 likecode 默认路由。

## 4. 配置优先级说明

```
环境变量 model routes
  > 标准 Claude settings modelRoutes
  > likecode settings modelRoutes

likecode 层级内部：
.claude/settings.likecode.local.json   （项目级，最高）
  > ~/.claude/settings.likecode.json   （用户全局，fallback）
```

